    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Arches or corbeled transitional elements that span the interior corners of a square or polygonal structure serving to support a circular or polygonal superstructure.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
